<br>
If your worried about not benig organized enough, I'd suggest this:<br>
<br>
Get her solo<br>
A few hefty tanks (4.5k+ hp melee) run up and engage, pin her on a wall (watch book shelves). <br>
After first AE, ALL melee and their clerics run into the fray. Clerics chain cast AE heals. WoRedemption if you got it.<br>
Meanwhile, *everyone* else nukes. Wizzies, Mages, Druids, Shaman, Necro, enchanters.<br>
<br>
She's only got 16k hp or so, and damn near every nuke will land for full. <br>
<br>
<br>
What you suggested though....prolly wouldn't work, and people really do like trying new things now and then =) <p><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=141811">Zantaer
